snippet.title: Wish Talk Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Wish Talk is a social sim "powered by a cutting-edge deep learning AI." Set on a magical island, you'll befriend toy characters and learn more about them through free-form conversations. Wish Talk recently had a playtest on Steam. Did any of you get the chance to try it? https://store.steampowered.com/app/1853370/Wish_Talk #indiegames #gaming #cozygames
